results.deck: Volition, now a subsidiary of Koch Media, is the development studio behind Red Faction and Saints Row.
results.description:
Volition Studios was originally a part of Parallax, the studio behind the classic Descent series. After flagging sales of the Freespace series resulted in Volition being acquired by THQ, they went on to have much greater success with the Red Faction series, and more recently, the Saints Row franchise. As of January 23, 2013, they were acquired by Koch Media in THQ's fire sale and are now called Deep Silver Volition.
